    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as a project car or for parts. It currently has major engine trouble and a transmission that slips, meaning it is not reliably drivable in its current state. The body has several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and some rust spots. The interior also shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional radio. It will need a dedicated owner ready to invest time and money into significant repairs.",
