      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on a smooth, comfortable ride from day one. Whether you're just ziping around town or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is totally ready for its next adventure with you. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example retains its factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and features a recently serviced variable M differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a high-pressure VANOS system overhaul and recent valve adjustment. Experience the pinnacle of hydraulic steering feedback and a chassis balanced for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Reliable used car. Good condition. Clean title. Routine maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the ideal balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior finish presents beautifully with a deep, consistent gloss, showing only minor, localized stone chips on the lower front valance and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014imperfections that are purely cosmetic and expected for its age. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the leather upholstery is supple with minimal creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or cracks. All interior electronics, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and premium audio system, have been tested and are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It features a recently serviced powertrain with a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a set of Michelin tires with approximately 80% tread life remaining. The brake pads and rotors were replaced last season, ensuring firm and responsive stopping power. This has been a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle, and it comes with a complete set of owner's manuals and two sets of keys. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and is ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
