      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience and dependable performance. Every system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our standards for roadworthiness and longevity. We invite you to inspect this exceptional example of automotive engineering, which offers a sophisticated balance of utility and prestige.",
      "price": 34500.0,
